Testing Hash Code

  Matchers for ensuring properties influence the generated hash code.

+---
import static com.google.code.beanmatchers.BeanMatchers.*;
...
assertThat(BeanToTest.class, hasValidBeanHashCode());

assertThat(BeanToTest.class, hasValidBeanHashCodeFor("testOnlyThisProperty"));

assertThat(BeanToTest.class, hasValidBeanHashCodeExcluding("dontTestPropertyWithThisName"));
